  "title": "Senior Electrician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>· Install, maintain and repair wiring, lighting, CCTV systems, switches, sockets etc.</p><p>· Able to troubleshooting and test to ensure functionality and safety compliance</p><p>· Collaborate with project teams to complete installations on schedule and within budget</p><p>· Know how to read and execute based on drawings and single-line diagrams</p><p>· Conduct quality checks to ensure installations meet company standards </p><p>· Submit work report and technical records per company requirements </p><p>· Adhere to all safety protocols and electrical codes at all times</p><p>· Provide technical support and solutions to clients </p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Several years of work experiences especially in the renovation industry</p><p>· Familiar with relevant regulations and laws</p><p>· Valid Electrician license and relevant safety certification</p><p>· Ability to read and interpret technical drawings</p><p>· Possess strong communication, problem-solving and troubleshooting skills</p><p>· Ability to work independently <br /></p><p>* 6-day work week, 9am to 6pm. Willing to work on Sundays and PH where necessary. <br />Location: All around Singapore. Transport allowance will be covered. </p>",
